Comment: The same puzzle was published previously and the comments provided there haven't been addressed in this version.

Please don't reuse your previous puzzle as a new one while ignoring the feedback provided there.

Input
* Please change "the number" to "a positive integer".

Constraints
* Please add:

[[N]] has at most 200 digits.

Stub generator
* Please change 1000 to 200.

Cover picture
* Consider uploading a cover picture for the puzzle.

Cases
* There are no UNLUCKY cases.

* Some tests are not similar to their validators.

* Cases where a number that contains 0s and 5s except for one digit should be added.

* Other cases needed as mentioned in my comments on that previous version.

Thanks.
